title: James E. Reid Design I Love Norwegian Buhunds License Plate Frame
features: Made in the United States of high-impact black acrylic plastic and quality exterior-grade vinyl
This frame will fit standard 12" x 6" license plates used in USA, Canada, and Mexico. Screws are not included.
